                "questionText": "Cho hai biểu thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fa3a3c35-b93c-4247-b122-5b3f9049bf23.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/47f40841-df17-400f-b6c9-5670a418f7f2.png\"/> với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/604d066f-2f82-4176-a1b7-70e2699a8153.png\"/>\n<br>1. Tính giá trị của biểu thức <i>A</i> khi <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/897163be-712e-4e67-99fa-a62099d29530.png\"/>\n<br>2. Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/f83f091c-2445-4cb2-a813-58cf177d161d.png\"/>\n<br>3. Đặt <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/e2ec69f8-1013-4c8b-a658-3d3dd3a35753.png\"/> Tìm x nguyên nhỏ nhất để <i>P</i> có giá trị là số nguyên.\n",
                "answer": "1) Thay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/30d4069e-e613-44c3-bc58-c7ce8282521c.png\"/> vào biểu thức <i>A</i>, ta có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/65d7a2ed-fa35-4edc-97f2-f62f4f21362b.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/6cfa323b-fb7f-458f-b990-6e541993ffd7.png\"/>\n<br>2) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/4b5e2e16-2b4a-4706-8c70-23c1b02c0b1f.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/059b6664-898d-4751-a3cd-ef4136086268.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/bbc28c78-8d4a-4f6e-9661-79edf739afb4.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/736201ea-b3b0-4b45-ac79-095064160f0b.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/00188e14-8d4d-4c8f-9af4-2eaa028322d3.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/8f748839-3a3c-446f-81b2-d818c0fe4b8f.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1526f6e3-f6f2-4b54-a938-8edd17f1ea42.png\"/>\n<br>3) Với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/772e50cb-5993-4796-b8a9-eea4797804bd.png\"/> ta có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/b04ebe8d-a5e5-470d-b0d5-a6c53493eef8.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/f3da2cbb-b2ab-45cf-822d-02aea567fcd8.png\"/>\n<br><i>P</i> nguyên khi <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/b768f7f6-ad7d-402f-96d4-cdd32ee49db7.png\"/> nguyên, suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/25392911-aa0b-46c6-83de-c51d42dbbdea.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a28afc99-8a23-46d2-91e7-ae4e84ac5483.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/af9879e2-89d1-4e37-99e4-454439822515.png\"/>\n<br>Mà <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/f426f2ae-c28d-43c9-aa17-793ad7b43214.png\"/> và <i>x </i>là số nguyên nhỏ nhất\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/549b3597-9558-4dc9-a570-38fdcc795eeb.png\"/>\n",
